=== 专业评价 ===
[[AllMusic|AllMusic]]的{{le|斯蒂芬·托马斯·艾尔维恩|Stephen Thomas Erlewine}}在评价《[[第五辑|第五辑]]》时写道，专辑最好的地方“就像他们的其他歌曲那样，魔力红在创作《甜心》时拥抱他们一直以来所做的和谐的、略带深情的成人当代流行音乐乐队<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/v-mw0002704238|title=V - Maroon 5|publisher=AllMusic. All Media Group|last=Erlewine|first=Stephen Thomas|accessdate=2015-01-13|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141221134020/http://www.allmusic.com/album/v-mw0002704238|archivedate=2014-12-21}}</ref>。”[[VH1|VH1]]的爱丽莎·泰杰（{{lang|en|Alexa Tietjen}}）指出，该曲是一首“让电台喜爱的流行歌”<ref name="Video Premiere"/>。{{le|Idolator|Idolator (website}}的迈克·瓦斯（{{lang|en|Mike Wass}}）将歌曲标榜为“可笑得吸引人的果酱”<ref name="cover idolator">{{cite web|last=Wass|first=Mike|title=Maroon 5 Unveil The Cover Of Breezy New Single 'Sugar' Tease Stills From The Feel-Good Video|url=http://www.idolator.com/7576742/maroon-5-sugar-cover-art-video-stills|work=''Idolator''|publisher=SpinMedia|accessdate=2015-01-14|date=2015-01-13|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150115080234/http://www.idolator.com/7576742/maroon-5-sugar-cover-art-video-stills|archivedate=2015-01-15}}</ref>。同样，《{{le|国民报 (迪拜)|The National (Abu Dhabi)|国民报}}》的赛义德·赛义德（{{lang|en|Saeed Saeed}}）称歌曲是《第五辑》的亮点，并接着表示歌曲“副歌的靶心会让你立刻跟着哼唱<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thenational.ae/arts-lifestyle/music/album-review-maroon-5--v|title=Album review: Maroon 5 – V|last=Saeed|first=Saeed|work=The National|date=2014-09-22|accessdate=2015-10-13|archive-date=2016-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160220200616/http://www.thenational.ae/arts-lifestyle/music/album-review-maroon-5--v|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”[[PopMatters|PopMatters]]的安妮·高尔文（{{lang|en|Annie Galvin}}）称赞了这首歌，并写道：“歌曲在游丝般的合成器上分层叠加了微妙时髦的吉他脉搏，击中了甜蜜的地方，而莱文许多歌的上限是悦耳动听<ref name="popmatters"/>。”差评方面，《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》的安德森称歌曲“空洞之余兼杂乱”<ref name="entertainmentweekly"/>。

=== 商业表现 ===
《第五辑》发行后，歌曲便在韩国国际榜和韩国Gaon榜分别空降并最高排至第13位<ref name="skic">{{cite web |url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/chart/digital.php?f_type=week&f_year=2014&f_month=&f_week=37&f_chart_kind_cd=E |title=Gaon Chart |publisher=Gaon |accessdate=2015-01-13 |language=ko|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217225451/http://www.gaonchart.co.kr/chart/digital.php?f_type=week&f_year=2014&f_month=&f_week=37&f_chart_kind_cd=E|archivedate=2014-12-17}}</ref>和第77位<ref name="skc">{{cite web |url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/chart/digital.php?f_chart_kind_cd=T&f_week=37&f_year=2014&f_type=week |title=Gaon Chart |publisher=Gaon|accessdate=2015-01-13 |language=ko|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217200359/http://www.gaonchart.co.kr/chart/digital.php?f_chart_kind_cd=T&f_week=37&f_year=2014&f_type=week|archivedate=2014-12-17}}</ref>。歌曲及其录影带发行后，便在数字媒体上获得关注。《[[公告牌_(杂志)|公告牌]]》预测歌曲首周凭借15多万份的数字销量空降前25位已成定局<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6443595/new-maroon-5-kelly-clarkson-singles-headed-for-debuts-on-hot-100|title=The band's 'Sugar' should sweeten the chart in the top 25, while Clarkson's 'Heartbeat Song' is also set to thump its way in|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|last1=Trust|first1=Gary|last2=Caulfield|first2=Keith|date=2015-01-16|accessdate=2015-01-17|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150120012216/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6443595/new-maroon-5-kelly-clarkson-singles-headed-for-debuts-on-hot-100|archivedate=2015-01-20}}</ref>。截至2015年1月31日当周，歌曲空降[[公告牌百强单曲榜|公告牌百强单曲榜]]第八名，成为魔力红第三首空降该榜前十的歌曲，而他们之前的单曲《[[Moves_Like_Jagger|Moves Like Jagger]]》空降该榜第八，而《[[公共电话_(歌曲)|公告电话]]》成绩更优秀，空降第三<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6443847/mark-ronson-bruno-mars-top-hot-100|title=Mark Ronson, Bruno Mars Top Hot 100, Maroon 5 Debuts at No. 8|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|last=Trust|first=Gary|date=2015-01-21|accessdate=2015-01-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150122054756/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6443847/mark-ronson-bruno-mars-top-hot-100|archivedate=2015-01-22}}</ref>。最终，歌曲成为乐队第11首前十热歌，成绩总体上排第八<ref name="yahoo">{{cite web|url=https://www.yahoo.com/music/maroon-5s-sugar-rushes-to-the-top-10-108767996651.html|title=Maroon 5's 'Sugar' Rushes to the Top 10|publisher=Chart Watch. Yahoo! Music|last=Grein|first=Paul|date=2015-01-22|accessdate=2015-01-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150122051511/https://www.yahoo.com/music/maroon-5s-sugar-rushes-to-the-top-10-108767996651.html|archivedate=2015-01-22}}</ref>。歌曲连续占据该榜第二名四个星期，直逼[[马克·朗森|马克·朗森]]搭档[[布鲁诺·马尔斯|布鲁诺·马尔斯]]的《[[Uptown_Funk|Uptown Funk]]》。在前十位呆了21个星期后，到2015年6月27日，歌曲滑至第10至12名。这标志着乐队在该榜前十呆过的最长时间，而之前的《Moves Like Jagger》和《[[最后一夜|最后一夜]]》也坚守前十21周。截至2015年8月，歌曲在美国售出330万份<ref name=us_sales/>。

